{"tid":304894,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解老一代班人咁中意借錢俾D濕鳩親戚???","createTime":"2017-07-01T08:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T12:41:42.000Z","uid":65429,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"823130dd0f9e9fb015b709b3fe477e451056cc7d","tid":304894,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"我老豆早幾年無條件借錢俾移民左向外國既姑媽做手術,明明果個姑媽有個仔做醫生但佢都照借<br />\n<br />\n之後有個仆街伯娘, 成日間唔中問我老豆借, 我老豆又借左俾佢, 仲要還少少其他唔還,明明佢D仔都出晒身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個D老餅問我老豆呢個細佬借錢<br />\n我老豆平時又對我唔大方都算<br />\n起碼佢係儲住D錢, 將來點都係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔明上一代D人咁重視親戚關係把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔借咪唔借囉, 唔通你係黑社會會搵人斬我咩"},{"pid":"729270a1bcdf92b10135c362f12f375f161d913a","tid":304894,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"西毒咁有錢 冇所謂la"},{"pid":"b7c07b72d076043869257bd1b5817ace109404c7","tid":304894,"uid":65429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"真係屌撚死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e3ff2cf1a9137de13a229e17362eee5c26f47c","tid":304894,"uid":65429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西毒咁有錢 冇所謂la</blockquote><br />\n好嬲囉, 唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c1405393e68f3bd2f0c417394325163c31bfd0","tid":304894,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"中國人重情"},{"pid":"8d97fbccb54f8b2f578209cef74db6c30f8ce7fe","tid":304894,"uid":65429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人重情</blockquote